{"tid":1626433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T09:59:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"35a9fd3087fff3e8017df2f17aa52d50cf5b3994","tid":1626433,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"昨日多區發生衝突事件，有示威者破壞工聯會的服務點，工聯會對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n有服務點破壞程度嚴重，未必能即時或數日內修復，對於部分服務未能即時恢復深感抱歉，並對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責，要求政府對暴徒繩之以法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484472-20191005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484472-20191005.htm&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=3dc0d1b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484472-20191005.htm&h=158d30e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484472-20191005.htm</a>"},{"pid":"72b84b0de5b1d4a5d917a1e2f5c4931b97abdba1","tid":1626433,"uid":258696,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暴動始祖"},{"pid":"ef3178ff36ff10ac63c3c51fa85cdcfd7b643517","tid":1626433,"uid":33176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"譴責埋67?"},{"pid":"a7a57a9ef66986c429b79914cffc21a1e92d95bd","tid":1626433,"uid":67325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"暴動KOL譴責真係别有一番風味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844fb77735cd63df521f00aea5ed7274ece52752","tid":1626433,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.fcchk.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/014.jpg\"